#Turn genome into 1 line of text, remove N's, all caps, add newline for EOF (required by str_split)
sed 's/N//g' ebola_zair.fasta | grep -v '^$\|^>' | tr -d '\n' | tr [a-z] [A-Z] > ez.txt
echo -e '\n' >> ez.txt 

#Add dependancies and snpeff database instructions


Published sources:	Mutation rate and genotype variation of ebola virus from mali case sequences (Science 04/15, Hoenen et al.)
			Probabilities of transversions and transitions (Molecular Biology 1976, Vol'kenshtein)

